            <h2 class="title">
              Impact Investing in India’s Social Stock Exchange: Why It’s the
              Future of Finance
            </h2>
            <div class="blog-meta-three">
              <ul class="list-wrap">
                <li><i class="far fa-calendar"></i>09 June, 2025</li>
                <li>
                  <img src="assets/img/blog/Blog Writer.png" alt="" /> by <a
